@startuml
title "Leave a Review"
start

:Navigate to SomeTrails;

:Find Trail;

:Click on "Review Trail";
if ( If Logged In ) then ( Yes )
else ( no )
    :Login / Register;
endif

:Give stars;
:Add Tags;
:Add Comments & Pics;
:Rate Difficulty w/ tags;
:Rate Parking;
:Note Conditions;
:Give activity type, and date;
:Submit;


stop
@enduml
